                      \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                        \n                                \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                        \n                                \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                        \n                                \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n            \n    \n    \n        \n                \n                    \n                        \n                                    \u003cdiv id=\"article-body\" itemprop=\"articleBody\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA new pair of updated iPad models wasn’t the only thing Apple just unveiled. Just like in previous years, Apple has refreshed its lineup of iPhone and Apple Watch bands with some new Spring-inspired colors.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"a-new-season-of-colors-for-iphone-cases\"\u003e\n                        A New Season of Colors for iPhone Cases\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003eApple has added four new colors to its popular silicone case for the iPhone 16 lineup. You can now choose from Tangerine, Aquamarine, Peony, and Periwinkle.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThe cases are available for the iPhone 16, iPhone 16 Plus, iPhone 16 Pro, and iPhone 16 Pro Max. \u003ca href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MDGR4ZM/A/iphone-16-plus-silicone-case-with-magsafe-peony\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eEach case is $49\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"more-hues-to-choose-from-for-many-apple-watch-bands\"\u003e\n                        More Hues To Choose from for Many Apple Watch Bands\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003eApple’s wide variety of Apple Watch bands are a great complement to the wearable device. And four of the band options received new color choices.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eFirst up, the \u003ca href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MDN14AM/A/40mm-northern-lights-solo-loop-size-0\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSolo Loop\u003c/a\u003e is now available in Peony, Periwinkle, and Northern Lights. Since there is no buckle, you will need to use a fit guide to find the best size for you. The band is $49.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"621c-4526-81b629d0596f\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/every-apple-watch-band/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/choose-apple-watch-band.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/choose-apple-watch-band.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/choose-apple-watch-band.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/choose-apple-watch-band.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/choose-apple-watch-band.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/choose-apple-watch-band.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/choose-apple-watch-band.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/choose-apple-watch-band.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/choose-apple-watch-band.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1680\" height=\"840\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Selection of Apple Watch bands\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/choose-apple-watch-band.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/choose-apple-watch-band.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/every-apple-watch-band/\" title=\"Every Apple Watch Band Compared\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\tEvery Apple Watch Band Compared\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\u003cp\u003eStruggling to choose which Apple Watch band to choose? Here’s a description of every band option to help you find the best one for you.\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eJust like the Solo Loop, make sure to find the best size choice before buying a \u003ca href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MDL64AM/A/46mm-peony-braided-solo-loop-size-6\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eBraided Solo Loop\u003c/a\u003e. Three new color choices include Tangerine, Aquamarine, and Peony for the $99 band.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eAnother popular option is \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/why-prefer-apple-watch-sport-loop-over-other-bands/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eApple’s Sport Loop which is lightweight and easy to wear\u003c/a\u003e. You can choose from a new Periwinkle or Sage hue \u003ca href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MDV54AM/A/46mm-periwinkle-sport-loop\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eof the $49 band\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThe classic \u003ca href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MDT54AM/A/46mm-tangerine-sport-band-s-m\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e$49 Sports Band\u003c/a\u003e is also now available in Aquamarine, Tangerine, and Periwinkle.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eIf you have a bit more to spend and are looking for a luxurious band option, there are a pair of new Hermès bands. The \u003ca href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MDFU4AM/A/apple-watch-herm%C3%A8s-49mm-bleu-hydra-en-mer\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eBleu Hydra En Mer \u003c/a\u003eis for the Apple Watch Ultra and is $449 while the \u003ca href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MDFK4AM/A/apple-watch-herm%C3%A8s-42mm-noir-%C3%A9cru-toile-h-single-tour?fnode=7d07deca62ec7f1cb7c9d4e18beadf6511afb3d8602f16f034bf20e46e0460343a29055943c51faaf321166899d5ae2299d0d4e2fa1207662dc36880d224030b85934c51244d5318660123ee248bfe4c\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eNoir/Ecru Toile H Single Tour is $349\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"jazz-up-your-iphone-or-apple-watch\"\u003e\n                        Jazz Up Your iPhone or Apple Watch\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eApple’s fun and unique color options provide a great way to help your Apple Watch or iPhone stand out from the crowd. I always enjoy finding unique colors, especially for my Apple Watch, and my wallet likely won\u0026#39;t appreciate me after buying a new band or two.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
